---
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import BackButton from "../components/BackButton.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { site } from "../config/site";
import {
  BLOG_LANGS,
  filterPostsByLang,
  getPublishedPosts
} from "../lib/blog";

const posts = await getPublishedPosts();
const postsByLang = {
  ko: filterPostsByLang(posts, "ko"),
  en: filterPostsByLang(posts, "en")
};

const tagCountsByLang = {
  ko: new Set(postsByLang.ko.flatMap((post) => post.data.tags)).size,
  en: new Set(postsByLang.en.flatMap((post) => post.data.tags)).size
};
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About the author and this blog.">
  <Header />
  <BackButton href="/" />

  <main class="shell app-shell">
    <section class="app-panel about-panel">
      <div class="about-header">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">
            <span data-ui-lang="ko">소개</span>
            <span data-ui-lang="en">About</span>
          </p>
          <div class="about-name-row">
            <div class="about-avatar">
              <img
                src="https://github.com/achieveonepark.png"
                alt={site.author}
                width="40"
                height="40"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
            <h1>{site.author}</h1>
          </div>
          <p class="about-tagline">
            <span data-ui-lang="ko">Unity, Android, iOS, CI/CD, ASP.NET. 그리고 그 외 신기능이 궁금해서 경험을 기록하기 위한 블로그!</span>
            <span data-ui-lang="en">A blog for recording experiences with Unity, Android, iOS, CI/CD, ASP.NET, and other exciting new technologies!</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {BLOG_LANGS.map((lang) => (
        <div class="about-stats" data-ui-lang={lang}>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">{postsByLang[lang].length}</span>
            <span class="stat__label">{lang === "en" ? "Posts" : "글"}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">{tagCountsByLang[lang]}</span>
            <span class="stat__label">{lang === "en" ? "Tags" : "태그"}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>
          <span data-ui-lang="ko">소개</span>
          <span data-ui-lang="en">Overview</span>
        </h2>
        <p data-ui-lang="ko">
          8년 차 Unity 개발자로서 <strong>PC와 모바일 게임의 개발부터 런칭</strong>까지 전 과정을 경험했습니다.<br /><br />
          최근에는 <strong>기술 지원 조직</strong>에서 공용 시스템 구축과 개발 환경 개선을 통해 <strong>팀의 생산성을 높이는 데 주력</strong>하고 있습니다.<br /><br />
          <code>C#</code>을 사용하는 <code>Unity</code>와 <code>.NET</code> 환경에 능숙하며, 특히 <strong>동료들의 불편함을 해소</strong>하고 효율을 극대화하는 <strong>툴 개발</strong> 과정에서 큰 보람을 느낍니다.<br /><br />
          어린 시절 RPG를 좋아했던 순수한 열정을 바탕으로 게임 개발자가 되었으며, 항상 많은 게임을 즐깁니다.<br /><br />
          <strong>긴밀한 소통과 목표 공유가 최고의 결과를 만든다는 믿음을 갖고 동료들과 함께 성장하고 있습니다.</strong>
        </p>
        <p data-ui-lang="en">
          As a Unity developer with eight years of experience, I have worked through the full cycle of <strong>building and launching both PC and mobile games</strong>.<br /><br />
          More recently, I have been focused on <strong>improving team productivity</strong> through shared systems and better development workflows within a <strong>technical support organization</strong>.<br /><br />
          I am comfortable working in <code>Unity</code> and <code>.NET</code> environments with <code>C#</code>, and I find the most satisfaction in <strong>building tools</strong> that <strong>remove friction for teammates</strong> and make teams more effective.<br /><br />
          I became a game developer out of the same pure enthusiasm I had as a child when I loved RPGs, and I still spend a lot of time enjoying games myself.<br /><br />
          <strong>I believe the best results come from close communication and shared goals, and I keep growing together with the people around me.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>
          <span data-ui-lang="ko">기술 스택</span>
          <span data-ui-lang="en">Tech Stack</span>
        </h2>
        <ul class="tech-list">
          <li>Unity</li>
          <li>C#</li>
          <li>WebGL</li>
          <li>Steam</li>
          <li>Android</li>
          <li>iOS</li>
          <li>Firebase</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>
          <span data-ui-lang="ko">연락처</span>
          <span data-ui-lang="en">Contact</span>
        </h2>
        <ul class="contact-list">
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/achieveonepark" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              GitHub @achieveonepark
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-panel {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-name-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-avatar {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-avatar img {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent);
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .about-tagline {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--panel-soft);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .stat__num {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
    font-family: var(--font-code);
  }

  .stat__label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-section p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tech-list,
  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .tech-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .tech-list li::before {
    content: "▸";
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }

  .contact-list a {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-list a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

</style>
